### API requests for ff-trainingskarte
# Run with vscode-rest-client or similar tool

@host = http://localhost:8080

### List all vehicles (GET) → 200 OK
GET {{host}}/api/vehicles

### Create a vehicle (POST) → 201 CREATED, ADMIN required
### Request body: callsign (unique), type, status
POST {{host}}/api/vehicles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "callsign": "ELW-HH-1101",
  "type": "ELW 1",
  "status": 1
}

### Update a vehicle (PUT) → 200 OK, ADMIN required
PUT {{host}}/api/vehicles/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "callsign": "ELW-HH-1102",
  "type": "ELW 1",
  "status": 0
}

### Update vehicle position (PUT) → 200 OK, ADMIN required
### Coordinates must be within Hamburg area: lat [53.3–53.8], lng [9.6–10.4]
PUT {{host}}/api/vehicles/1/position
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lat": 53.5511,
  "lng": 9.9937
}

### Delete a vehicle (DELETE) → 204 No Content, ADMIN required
DELETE {{host}}/api/vehicles/1
